{"tid":1797332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"邊個再同我戴耳機就係便衣狗","createTime":"2019-12-25T10:24:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-25T10:47:47.000Z","uid":278698,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2a23874bb19eaaec551f3b05620657efdad104a2","tid":1797332,"uid":278698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T10:24:31.000Z","msg":"今晚邊個和理shop再戴耳機同其他狗狗聯絡<br />\n<br />\n繼而圍捕市民<br />\n<br />\n就會直接打入蓄牲道，永不超生"},{"pid":"c903083640db90fde18189d28df560d1add27ee8","tid":1797332,"uid":338262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T10:25:27.000Z","msg":"捕風捉影"},{"pid":"2ff57d05628bdae5ee48167dbc52f3eee3ddd156","tid":1797332,"uid":278698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T10:27:26.000Z","msg":"起碼唔比佢地咁易contact 自己人"},{"pid":"1028c1d7038476f16601bef5b269fa1562701668","tid":1797332,"uid":263618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T10:28:13.000Z","msg":"popo strategy<br />\n<br />\n1.啲便衣是但捉一件 然後附近啲人就會圍便衣救人 之後就可以名正言順話人襲警所以防暴入商場<br />\n<br />\n2. 忠誠勇毅嘅佢哋係唔怕經濟攬炒<br />\n怕經濟攬炒嘅只係施生陳生嗰啲收成期買晒鋪嘅人<br />\n呢個係上面嘅指令<br />\n佢地只會不斷咁樣irritate你<br />\n每隔一段時間就會irritate你<br />\n目的係想你哋開花，捉晒有膽量行動嘅人<br />\n剩返嗰啲今時今日都冇膽行出嚟嘅，將來23條呀國歌戲出咗之後更加唔會夠膽出聲，所以嗰啲人響上面來講係廢嘅，上面覺得只要捉實夠膽行出黎嘅就代表成功"},{"pid":"e144f12d91c50f8f167d62088b21c657e807af81","tid":1797332,"uid":49753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T10:28:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">邊個再屈戴耳機就係狗既，邊個就係分化割蓆，未審先判</span></span>"},{"pid":"76e8061515e8d83ed7507811a7d43a37c24ccc15","tid":1797332,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T10:29:09.000Z","msg":"點睇zella 民間報料電台？"},{"pid":"910d44ba922235474f79c3b66ac18ff03d653167","tid":1797332,"uid":276508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e144f12d91c50f8f167d62088b21c657e807af81","tid":1797332,"uid":49753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T10:28: